OL,3,CMan who burnt down MP's office denies
OL,4,Ctargeting politician
OL,6,FA man who admitted burning down an
OL,7,FMP's constituency office disputes that
OL,8,Fhe deliberately targeted the
OL,9,Fpolitician's premises, a court heard.
OL,11,FJosh Oliver, 28, had been living rough
OL,12,Fnear the offices of Sharon Hodgson,
OL,13,FLabour MP for Washington and Gateshead
OL,14,FSouth, when he set fire to a bin store
OL,15,Fat the building in September 2025.
OL,17,FAt a previous hearing before Newcastle
OL,18,FMagistrates, he admitted arson on the
OL,19,Fbasis that he was reckless.
