OL,3,CMan who burnt down MP's office denies
OL,4,Ctargeting politician
OL,6,FThe prosecution said CCTV images
OL,7,Ffilmed over the days preceding the
OL,8,Ffire showed Oliver breaking windows at
OL,9,FVermont House, damaging and eventually
OL,10,Fburgling the building before setting
OL,11,Ffire to the bin store.
OL,13,FMr Perks said the fire "took out the
OL,14,Fentire building".
OL,16,FAs well as serving as the MP's
OL,17,Fconstituency office, Vermont House
OL,18,Falso accommodated a veterans' mental
OL,19,Fhealth service operated by the NHS and
OL,20,Fa charity for people with extremely
OL,21,Frare genetic diseases.
