OL,3,CMan who burnt down MP's office denies
OL,4,Ctargeting politician
OL,6,FLee Fish, defending Oliver, who was
OL,7,Fnot in court, said: "He disputes he
OL,8,Fdeliberately targeted the Member of
OL,9,FParliament.
OL,11,F"He disputes he intended to set fire
OL,12,Fto the entire building.
OL,14,F"He said he was reckless."
OL,16,FThe court was told Oliver, who is in
OL,17,Fprison awaiting sentence, had not co-
OL,18,Foperated with the preparation of a
OL,19,Fpsychiatric report or engaged with
OL,20,Fprobation.
