OL,3,CMan who burnt down MP's office denies
OL,4,Ctargeting politician
OL,6,FRecorder Jeremy Barnett said a Newton
OL,7,FHearing, where the facts relating to
OL,8,Fthe guilty plea will be decided,
OL,9,Fshould take place on 9 March 2026.
OL,11,FThe arson charge stated that the
OL,12,Fdamage to Vermont House was estimated
OL,13,Fto be between #250,000 and #500,000.
OL,15,FOliver also admitted burgling the
OL,16,Fbuilding when he stole a mallet and
OL,17,Fpower tools on the night. He admitted
OL,18,Fthree counts of criminal damage,
OL,19,Fnamely smashing windows at Vermont
OL,20,FHouse, in the days before the fire.
